data.description: Experience the serenity of secluded living in the sought-after Berrydale community with the opportunity to own an expansive 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home situated on 15 acres along Manning Creek, all for just under $300,000! Built in 2017, this Live Oak manufactured home rests on a cleared acre, offering plenty of buildable land and promising hunting prospects. Revel in the peacefulness of this location, while still enjoying convenient access to grocery outlets for all your shopping needs.  Step inside to discover a contemporary open floor plan that encompasses a spacious, family-oriented living and dining room. The generous wrap-around kitchen, complete with an island, simplifies holiday gatherings. The thoughtful split floor plan ensures privacy, with the master bedroom featuring an attached full bathroom, complete with a walk-in closet, garden tub, and walk-in shower.  Two additional guest bedrooms share a full bathroom, while a Jr. Master bedroom boasts its own attached Jr. master bathroom. Please be mindful that the property is currently occupied until February 2024; hence, please refrain from disturbing the tenant. Embrace the essence of country living and schedule your viewing today!
